The paper presents a linear projection technique for discovering interpretable relationships in high-dimensional data. This falls under the category of machine learning and data analysis, which is covered by several sub-categories in arXiv CS. Specifically, cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.CV (Computer Vision) are likely categories as they are closely related to the topic of dimension reduction and data analysis. Additionally, cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) are also possible categories as they deal with large-scale data analysis and optimization, which are relevant to the proposed method.
